    <item>
      <title>Nvidia CEO 访问中国，参与北京反垄断调查和人工智能限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/nvidia-ceo-tours-china-during-beijing-antitrust-probe-ai-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋本周将前往中国，走访中国主要城市。目前，北京方面正在调查英伟达在国内的业务，而华盛顿方面则对其人工智能芯片的海外销售实施新的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/nvidia-ceo-tours-china-during-beijing-antitrust-probe-ai-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 禁令风险促使用户纷纷转向其他中国制造的应用程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/tiktok-substitutes-xiaohongshu-and-lemon8-top-iphone-download-charts-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 TikTok 即将被禁之前，用户纷纷寻找其替代品，而中国研发的两款社交应用小红书和 Lemon8 已占据苹果公司美国 iPhone 下载排行榜的前两名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/tiktok-substitutes-xiaohongshu-and-lemon8-top-iphone-download-charts-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 01:42:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国讨论将 TikTok US 出售给马斯克作为可能选项之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/china-discusses-sale-of-tiktok-us-to-musk-as-one-possible-option</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国官员正在评估一种潜在选择，即如果 TikTok 未能抵御针对这款短视频应用的有争议的禁令，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 将收购 TikTok 的美国业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/china-discusses-sale-of-tiktok-us-to-musk-as-one-possible-option</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 客户面临潜在延迟，iPhone 销量下降 5% | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/bloomberg-technology-01-13-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 关注了 Nvidia，因为有报道称这家芯片制造商的一些客户面临新的延误。此外，随着中国竞争加剧，苹果的 iPhone 销量在全球下降了 5%。此外，加州野火肆虐的最新情况以及 Lyft 等公司如何帮助救援工作。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/bloomberg-technology-01-13-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登高级助手沙利文称特朗普可能会保留新的人工智能芯片控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-likely-to-maintain-new-ai-chip-controls-top-biden-aide-jake-sullivan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府的一位高级官员表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普很可能会维持美国对英伟达公司等公司在全球销售人工智能芯片的新限制，理由是两党对中国追求先进技术存在国家安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-likely-to-maintain-new-ai-chip-controls-top-biden-aide-jake-sullivan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Databricks 获得 50 亿美元私人信贷和银行融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/databricks-inks-5-billion-financing-from-private-credit-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，软件制造商 Databricks Inc. 已从黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.)、阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 和 Blue Owl Capital Inc. 等贷方获得超过 50 亿美元的融资，这是其迄今为止最大规模的债务融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/databricks-inks-5-billion-financing-from-private-credit-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 19:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险资产遭抛售 比特币跌至 11 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bitcoin-falls-to-lowest-since-november-in-risk-asset-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债券收益率大幅上升，投资者抛售风险较高的资产，比特币跌至近两个月来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bitcoin-falls-to-lowest-since-november-in-risk-asset-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:43:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能投资者为何应该担心自动驾驶汽车事故</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-ai-investors-should-worry-about-the-self-driving-car-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[机器人出租车本应是自动化的简单部分。通用汽车的努力失败表明该行业距离实现其疯狂的承诺还有多远。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-ai-investors-should-worry-about-the-self-driving-car-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫公布对英伟达 AI 芯片出口的新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/white-house-unveils-new-curbs-on-exporting-nvidia-ai-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫宣布对英伟达公司及其同行的先进人工智能芯片销售实施全面的新限制，由特朗普政府决定如何以及是否实施遭到业界激烈反对的限制措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/white-house-unveils-new-curbs-on-exporting-nvidia-ai-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能表现令人失望，iPhone 假日季销量下降 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/iphone-sales-fall-in-2024-after-limited-apple-intelligence-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年最后一个季度，受产品升级不尽如人意以及竞争对手在中国市场进军的影响，苹果公司的 iPhone 销量全球下降了约 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/iphone-sales-fall-in-2024-after-limited-apple-intelligence-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
